Planning and Requirements Gathering
Understanding the data sources, databases, and specific requirements.
Data Collection and Profiling
Gathering metadata from databases and performing initial data profiling.
Analysis and Matching
Running data type matching, similarity checks (Levenshtein, Soundex, etc.), and Chi-square tests.
AI Integration (Optional)
Implementing AI-based analysis to find semantic similarity between columns.
Validation and Reporting
Finalizing the matches and presenting them in reports.
Maintenance and Support (Optional)
Ongoing updates or support to add new databases or enhance analysis.
